Synopsis

program [key1=]val1 [key2=]val2 .!.!.

Description

ZENO is Josh Barnes’ version of NEMO. The code is largely derived from NEMO. The binary datafiles, via flestruct(3NEMO) are largely compatible.

See Also

nemo(1NEMO)

Author

Josh Barnes

Further Information

http://www.ifa.hawaii.edu/faculty/barnes/zeno/index.html
